web views for specific international Wikipedia pages. So here in this example plot, you see that

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:15.760
the views for the Wiki page of the band 21 Pilots exploded dramatically in early 2016. I don't

00:07:15.760 --> 00:07:22.239
really know them. I don't know why that happened. But there are some interesting lag effects here

